These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
House: tower, victorian
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, trike
1. the tower house is on the left of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| House   | tower  | victorian |
| Transport     | trike | subway  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, kiwi
There are 2 different nationalities: thai, indian
1. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Food    | eggplant      | kiwi         |
| Nationality   | thai | indian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: writing, fishing
There 2 different types of food: orange, spinach
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Hobby   | fishing | writing   |
| Food       | spinach  | orange |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-4::.
There are 2 different nationalities: french, indonesian
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: azalea, tulip
1. the indonesian is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Nationality   | french  | indonesian |
| Flower         | azalea | tulip    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-5::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: february, october
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |   2    |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | sprite |
| Birthday   | october        | february  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-6::.
