.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-10::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, bolivar
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, hiking
1. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |   2    |
| Cigar   | davidoff        | bolivar    |
| Hobby      | card-games | hiking |

